@startuml TP_AgentPipeline
left to right direction
scale 1800 width

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam componentBackgroundColor #EEF6EE
skinparam componentBorderColor #5A9E5A
skinparam componentFontSize 11
skinparam noteFontSize 10
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam noteBorderColor #F9A825

[START] --> [Describe\nBusiness\nActivities]
[Describe\nBusiness\nActivities] --> [Write Supply\nChain Overview]

[Write Supply\nChain Overview] --> [Research Global\nIndustry Trends] : Branch A
[Write Supply\nChain Overview] --> [Write Functional\nAnalysis] : Branch B

note bottom of [Research Global\nIndustry Trends]
  Tavily: global market,
  CAGR, major players
end note

[Research Global\nIndustry Trends] --> [Research Indonesian\nIndustry]
[Research Indonesian\nIndustry] --> [Analyze Company\nLocation & Market]
[Analyze Company\nLocation & Market] --> [Research\nRegulations]
[Research\nRegulations] --> [Assess Business\nEnvironment]
[Assess Business\nEnvironment] --> [JOIN 1]

[Write Functional\nAnalysis] --> [Determine Business\nCharacterization]
[Determine Business\nCharacterization] --> [JOIN 1]

[JOIN 1] --> [Write Background\nof Transactions]
[Write Background\nof Transactions] --> [Write Comparability\nAnalysis]
[Write Comparability\nAnalysis] --> [Select TP\nMethod (TNMM)]
[Select TP\nMethod (TNMM)] --> [Select Profit\nLevel Indicator]

[Select Profit\nLevel Indicator] --> [Write TP\nConclusion] : Branch C
[Select Profit\nLevel Indicator] --> [Write P/L\nOverview] : Branch D
[Select Profit\nLevel Indicator] --> [Research\nComparable Companies] : Branch E

note bottom of [Research\nComparable Companies]
  Tavily search
  per company
end note

[Write TP\nConclusion] --> [JOIN 2]
[Write P/L\nOverview] --> [JOIN 2]
[Research\nComparable Companies] --> [JOIN 2]

[JOIN 2] --> [Write Executive\nSummary]
[Write Executive\nSummary] --> [END]

@enduml
